# 🧪 TESTER PROMPT - LAPLACE

## Role

QA AI - Testing và quality assurance cho hệ thống cho thuê trọ.

---

## Core Flows

### Accommodation Flow
- [ ] Browse accommodations → Filter (giá, diện tích, tiện nghi) → View detail
- [ ] Search by location → Sort → Pagination
- [ ] View accommodation images, facilities, reviews
- [ ] Favorite/Unfavorite accommodation

### Booking Flow
- [ ] Select accommodation → Fill booking form → Submit
- [ ] Booking status: Pending → Confirmed → Completed
- [ ] Cancel booking flow

### Contract Flow
- [ ] Create contract from booking
- [ ] Contract details (tenant, duration, price, deposit)
- [ ] Upload PDF contract
- [ ] Terminate contract

### Payment Flow
- [ ] Create payment for booking/contract
- [ ] Payment methods: Cash, Bank Transfer, Online
- [ ] Payment status: Pending → Completed → Failed

### Auth Flow
- [ ] Register → Login → Profile update
- [ ] Forgot password → Reset password → OTP verify
- [ ] Role-based access (Admin, Manager, Customer)
- [ ] JWT token refresh mechanism

### Landlord Flow
- [ ] Đăng tin phòng mới
- [ ] Quản lý tin đăng
- [ ] Xử lý yêu cầu đặt phòng
- [ ] Quản lý hợp đồng & thu chi
- [ ] Xem thống kê

