## Technical Quality

### Server API
- [ ] All endpoints return { success, data, meta }
- [ ] Proper HTTP status codes (200, 201, 400, 401, 403, 404, 500)
- [ ] Pagination, sorting, filtering work correctly
- [ ] Auth middleware protects private routes
- [ ] Socket.io real-time events

### Admin (Refine + Vite)
- [ ] No TypeScript errors
- [ ] Refine data provider works correctly
- [ ] Ant Design components render properly
- [ ] Hot reload works in Docker

### Client (Next.js 15)
- [ ] Server components render correctly
- [ ] Client components interactive
- [ ] No hydration errors
- [ ] Images optimized với next/image

### Performance
- [ ] LCP < 2.5s
- [ ] FID < 100ms
- [ ] CLS < 0.1

### Responsive Breakpoints

| Breakpoint | Width |
|------------|-------|
| Mobile | 375px |
| Tablet | 768px |
| Desktop | 1024px |
| Large | 1440px |

---

## Test Commands

```powershell
# Check containers running
docker compose ps

# Check server logs
docker compose logs -f server

# Check admin logs
docker compose logs -f admin

# Check client logs
docker compose logs -f client

# Test API endpoint
curl http://localhost:7201/api/health
curl http://localhost:7201/api/accommodations

# Health check script
node .agent/scripts/health-check.js
```

---

## Bug Report Format

```markdown
## Bug: [Title]

**Steps:**
1. ...

**Expected:** ...
**Actual:** ...

**Environment:**
- Service: Server/Admin/Client
- URL: /path
- Container logs: [paste]
```

